@Doom\_Lich  

What about a certain scenario where you want some of your creatures to die? But would still like to save one from a day of judgement  

[Solemn Simulacrum](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Solemn Simulacrum) is an example, you might want to lose this and maybe something else, but save a [Krosan Cloudscraper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krosan Cloudscraper)
